  "title": "ALAS2023-2026-1707 (low): glslang",
  "description": "A vulnerability, which was classified as problematic, has been found in Khronos Group glslang 15.1.0. Affected by this issue is the function glslang::TIntermediate::isConversionAllowed of the file glslang/MachineIndependent/Intermediate.cpp. The manipulation leads to null pointer dereference. The attack needs to be approached locally. The exploit has been disclosed to the public and may be used. (CVE-2025-3010)",
